11#include "modules/audio_coding/codecs/pcm16b/audio_decoder_pcm16b.h"

13#include <utility>
14
15#include "modules/audio_coding/codecs/legacy_encoded_audio_frame.h"
16#include "modules/audio_coding/codecs/pcm16b/pcm16b.h"
17#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21AudioDecoderPcm16B::AudioDecoderPcm16B(int sample_rate_hz, size_t num_channels)
22 : sample_rate_hz_(sample_rate_hz), num_channels_(num_channels) {
23 RTC_DCHECK(sample_rate_hz == 8000 || sample_rate_hz == 16000 ||
24 sample_rate_hz == 32000 || sample_rate_hz == 48000)
25 << "Unsupported sample rate " << sample_rate_hz;
26 RTC_DCHECK_GE(num_channels, 1);
27}
28
29void AudioDecoderPcm16B::Reset() {}
30
31int AudioDecoderPcm16B::SampleRateHz() const {
32 return sample_rate_hz_;
33}
34
35size_t AudioDecoderPcm16B::Channels() const {
36 return num_channels_;
37}
38
39int AudioDecoderPcm16B::DecodeInternal(const uint8_t* encoded,
40 size_t encoded_len,
41 int sample_rate_hz,
42 int16_t* decoded,
43 SpeechType* speech_type) {
44 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(sample_rate_hz_, sample_rate_hz);
45 size_t ret = WebRtcPcm16b_Decode(encoded, encoded_len, decoded);
46 *speech_type = ConvertSpeechType(1);
47 return static_cast<int>(ret);
48}
49
50std::vector<AudioDecoder::ParseResult> AudioDecoderPcm16B::ParsePayload(
51 rtc::Buffer&& payload,
52 uint32_t timestamp) {
53 const int samples_per_ms = rtc::CheckedDivExact(sample_rate_hz_, 1000);
54 return LegacyEncodedAudioFrame::SplitBySamples(
55 this, std::move(payload), timestamp, samples_per_ms * 2 * num_channels_,
56 samples_per_ms);
57}
58
59int AudioDecoderPcm16B::PacketDuration(const uint8_t* encoded,
60 size_t encoded_len) const {
61 // Two encoded byte per sample per channel.
62 return static_cast<int>(encoded_len / (2 * Channels()));
63}

65} // namespace webrtc
